description:
Welcome to my course on "Learn Chi-Square from beginning to advance level" . This course will cover the complete understanding of Chi-Sqiuare with Hypothesis Testing in Statistics . In this course students will learn the numerically and theoratically concepts of Chi-Square. And also they can download material in the form of PDF Files .

With a lot of Examples that will clear the concepts of Chi-Square , and they will learn how to solve the questions of Hypothesis Testing and Goodness of fit test and its limitations.
title: Learn Chi-Square from beginning to advance level
